# Derived scorecard collection cache (regenerable via scorecard-collect.mjs; per-page detector findings + timing)
/.scorecard-cache/
# Derived browser-mode ceiling cache (regenerable via scorecard-browser-ceiling.mjs)
/.ceiling-cache/
# Dev-corpus screenshots (derived; regenerated deterministically from the committed dev HTML)
/corpus/.shots/
# NOTE: /corpus/dev/ is intentionally COMMITTED (not ignored). Live-web captures can't be reproduced byte-for-byte
# later, so the gated, Codex-labeled, detector-developed dev corpus must be a frozen content-addressable artifact -
# same precedent as the committed frozen-90 corpus HTML. The dev-manifest.json shas pin exactly what was captured.
